    "description": "You are the Robocide 3000 Custodial Unit. Your job is to clean the planet we are sending you to. By any means necessary, with prejudice. Enjoy the unlimited robotic carnage in this third person action game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339700/extras/e48579e221b74ab9c3ba812ceac54cd1.avif?t=1700158775\" width=615 height=120 /></span><br><br>You have many tools to traverse this planet, such as the Grappling Hook and Jet Pack. Use them wisely to explore the many unusual features of this world.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339700/extras/da4a6d89a25d258b5200c1e4a9985a8d.poster.avif?t=1700158775\" width=610 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339700/extras/da4a6d89a25d258b5200c1e4a9985a8d.webm?t=1700158775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339700/extras/da4a6d89a25d258b5200c1e4a9985a8d.mp4?t=1700158775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There are many biologicals to remove, nasty ones. Your Laser Rifle and Electric Saber will be the initial tools to use, but you can find and craft many other weapons you may find effective.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339700/extras/1f687207524d349a53a92254357aaf30.poster.avif?t=1700158775\" width=610 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339700/extras/1f687207524d349a53a92254357aaf30.webm?t=1700158775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339700/extras/1f687207524d349a53a92254357aaf30.mp4?t=1700158775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>It’s not enough to just remove the bio-infestation on the planet. You must also destroy their buildings and any other reminder of them. Wiped completely from existence, nice and clean!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339700/extras/5febecba27f90a92002638058788a3b0.poster.avif?t=1700158775\" width=610 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339700/extras/5febecba27f90a92002638058788a3b0.webm?t=1700158775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339700/extras/5febecba27f90a92002638058788a3b0.mp4?t=1700158775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>So now is the time to power up your energy cells and get ready to demolish everyone and everything in your path! As effectively and efficiently as you can, grind this planet into dust!",
